## How to use

1.  Sarvam TTS

``` python
import os
from dotenv import load_dotenv
from sarvamai.client import *

load_dotenv()
client = Sarvam(
  api_key=os.getenv("SARVAM_API_KEY"),
)
audio = client.text_to_speech(
    "Hello folks, how is the Josh?",
    "en-IN",
    speaker="karun",
    pitch=0,
    pace=1.0 ,
    model="bulbul:v2",
)
play(audio)
```

